  {
    "text": "- Dee!\n- Ha-ha!",
    "from": "0:06",
    "to": "0:08",
    "cn": "- 迪伊！\n- 哈哈！"
  },
  {
    "text": "# Yakka Dee, Yakka Dee, Yakka Dee!",
